--        Comment says "12 / 3 = 4, then 4 / 2 = 2 вҶ’ Just 2" вҖ” correct!
--        oops example: safeDivide 12 0 = Nothing, then Nothing >>= ... = Nothing вң“
--      - List: concatMap example unchanged, correct. вң“
--   4. No monad/functor confusion? None. вң“
