-- OBSERVATIONS (v0.2-aware)
-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ

вҠў= obs-gauntlet-pattern
  yield observation
  вҠў= observation вҶҗ "MULTI-ORACLE GAUNTLET IS A CANONICAL CELL PATTERN: N independent oracle cells check different quality dimensions of the same output. A crystallized aggregator (вҠў= conjunction) determines pass/fail. The вҠўвҲҳ loop re-runs ALL oracles after each targeted rewrite, ensuring fixes in one dimension don't break another. This is analogous to a full regression test suite after a bug fix вҖ” but for semantic quality dimensions, not just code correctness. The gauntlet scales: adding a 6th oracle (e.g., oracle-pedagogical) requires zero changes to existing oracles, just a new given in the gauntlet cell."

вҠў= obs-parallel-oracles-confluence
  yield observation
  вҠў= observation вҶҗ "PARALLEL ORACLE EXECUTION FROM CONFLUENCE: all 5 oracle cells depend only on explainвҶ’explanation (and optionally topicвҶ’subject or topicвҶ’audience). They share no inter-oracle dependencies. Kahn's algorithm places all 5 in the ready set simultaneously. Under parallel execution, all 5 could run concurrently вҖ” the confluence theorem (eval_diamond in Lean) guarantees identical results regardless of scheduling. This is the practical payoff of Cell's dataflow model: parallelism for free. No locks, no coordination, no race conditions."

вҠў= obs-crystallized-aggregator
  yield observation
  вҠў= observation вҶҗ "CRYSTALLIZED AGGREGATOR VALIDATES THE CRYSTALLIZATION BOUNDARY: gauntlet is в–ё crystallized because aggregation is pure logic вҖ” boolean conjunction, list filtering, list concatenation. All operations are v0.2 вҠў= primitives (and, not, filter, concat). No LLM judgment needed. This demonstrates the crystallization boundary: oracles are soft (require semantic judgment to CHECK quality), but their aggregation is hard (deterministic combination of boolean verdicts). Verification crystallizes before computation вҖ” the oracles judge, the gauntlet merely tallies."

вҠў= obs-targeted-rewrite-efficiency
  yield observation
  вҠў= observation вҶҗ "TARGETED REWRITE PREVENTS REGRESSION: the rewrite cell receives failed-oracles[] and failure-report[] from the gauntlet. It rewrites ONLY the parts that failed (safeDivide argument order), preserving what passed (structure, facts, tone, logic). The вҠўвҲҳ re-run of ALL oracles then VERIFIED this preservation вҖ” iteration 1 confirmed all 5 dimensions pass simultaneously. This is more efficient than full regeneration and structurally prevents regression. The gauntlet pattern makes the 'fix one thing, break another' anti-pattern detectable by construction."

вҠў= obs-aspirational-oracles-clean-separation
  yield observation
  вҠў= observation вҶҗ "v0.2 ASPIRATIONAL ORACLE SEMANTICS CLEAN UP THE GAUNTLET: explain has its own oracles (word count, code examples) that are aspirational under вҠўвҲҳ management. The 5 oracle cells in the through-chain are the OPERATIONAL quality gates вҖ” they feed into the gauntlet aggregator, which feeds the until condition. Without v0.2's clarification, explain's own oracles might trigger вҠЁ? retry BEFORE the gauntlet even runs, conflicting with the вҠўвҲҳ loop. The two mechanisms (oracle retry vs evolution loop) are now cleanly separated: explain's oracles are feedback signals, the gauntlet's verdict is the gate."

вҠў= obs-expression-language-audit
  yield observation
  вҠў= observation вҶҗ "v0.2 вҠў= EXPRESSION LANGUAGE AUDIT: R16's gauntlet used collect() вҖ” an undefined function. R17 replaces it with filter() on a parallel list of names and booleans, using only v0.2 primitives (filter, not, concat, and). The boolean conjunction for all-pass uses 'and' (v0.2 boolean primitive) instead of the mathematical вҲ§ symbol. concat() for failure-report was already valid (v0.2 list primitive). This audit makes the hard/soft boundary honest: every вҠў= expression is genuinely deterministic, evaluable without LLM judgment."

вҠў= obs-file-scope-recovery
  yield observation
  вҠў= observation вҶҗ "v0.2 FILE-SCOPE вҠЁ? AS SAFETY NET: the file-scope вҠЁ? (retry 3, partial-accept best) was never triggered because (a) individual cells didn't fail their oracles, and (b) the вҠўвҲҳ loop converged in 2 iterations. But it provides a clean fallback hierarchy: cell-level вҠЁ? on rewrite (retry with failure-report) handles rewrite failures, file-scope вҠЁ? catches everything else. If the gauntlet couldn't converge after 5 iterations, the best partial result (highest number of passing oracles) would be accepted rather than producing вҠҘ."

вҠў= obs-convergence-trajectory
  yield observation
  вҠў= observation вҶҗ "FAST CONVERGENCE FROM MOSTLY-CORRECT GENERATION: the initial explanation passed 4 of 5 oracles. Only oracle-semantic found an error (safeDivide argument order вҖ” a subtle Haskell currying mistake). The targeted rewrite fixed exactly that, and the full re-run confirmed no regression. 2 iterations out of max 5. Fast convergence is expected when (a) the initial generation is mostly correct, (b) fixes are targeted rather than wholesale rewrites, and (c) quality dimensions are orthogonal enough that fixing one doesn't break another. The gauntlet pattern amortizes well: more oracles means more checks per iteration but also more confidence per pass."
